data.title: Among Friends: MAME INTERACTIVE at Palm Springs Cultural Center, Palm Springs Cultural Center
data.meta_description: AUNTIE MAME Interactive Movie Event (original 1958 movie) Join us first for the third annual Mame's 1920's Themed cocktail party at 6:00. Come dressed up (or not) like the characters in the cocktail party in the movie or holiday attire. We will have multiple bars set up to serve you in style. Then at 8:00 join us in the theater for an interactive version of Auntie Mame. Now the movie you love comes alive with audience participation, live actions, and surprises. Be ready for a sell out engagement. Let's pack the houseAdvanced Tickets $15.43
